00:03:47.719 --> 00:03:54.864
remove the water from the wine, then pack this into his ship, the wine with the water

00:03:54.894 --> 00:04:02.594
removed, and then add water to the concentrated wine at his destination, then he

00:04:02.594 --> 00:04:07.384
