It was actually to treat high blood pressure and chest pain.

00:08:34.339 --> 00:08:39.914
It was created in a laboratory, and various tests were run with a small group of people.

00:08:41.274 --> 00:08:44.544
They wanted to test whether this drug was going to be

00:08:44.544 --> 00:08:48.274
a miracle cure for high blood pressure and chest pain.

